author: beatrice.acasandrei@softvision.com
text: Not sheriff results should be filter out in Performance Tab (hide results where the field shouldAlert is false - this field can be found in the PerformanceSignature model).  *Acceptance criteria:* Any performance metrics from a task that are not sheriffed are not displayed in Treeherder’s performance tab. For example, many tasks have a result for “fetch_content”, which is not sheriffed.  https://mozilla-hub.atlassian.net/browse/FXP-1884
